transcript:
the biggest misconception that people
have is that you need to be motivated in
order to take action but the thing is
you don't psychological studies actually
show that the exact opposite is true
research has shown that motivation
follows action not the other way around
so you don't need to feel good or feel
motivated to take action what you need
to do is you need to take action in
order to give yourself a chance at
feeling good and feeling motivated
